The weather so - chill, chilly really penguin feather roll ❄️

Winter is coming, but Central Florida stays hot 🔥 

There’s been a lot of chatter about the market lately - I’ve heard from plenty of buyers that they don’t want to buy a home at their current prices, sellers that don’t want to let go if their interest rate, and agents that are afraid they’ll have to get out of the real estate game 😳😩

My truth: The only thing that will ever really stop you, is yourself. 

Buyers: When you’re ready, don’t hesitate - if you try to time the market, you’ll probably lose 🙃

Sellers: Evaluate your motivation to move. There’s ways to find you better interest rates when buying a new home - plus, you can get a premium price for your home on the current market 🤑

Agents: Don’t give up, get creative! There are always new avenues to take to create relationships, and methods to improve your business. Take it from me, who took it from zero to hero and never gave up - if I can do it, you can too.

What’s concerning you about this current market, whether you’re a buyer, seller, agent, or on the sidelines watching? Comment below ⬇️👌
